 The vortex to cybertron flickered. Out of it came to old bots. They had 
journied to cybertron in search of victory and found defeat. Thier old leader 
magmatron had betrayed them and doing so is losing the war. They ahd to warn 
them. At one time this bot was called bobertron. A honorable destron. Now a 
primal. And the one still known as pantron also a primal. Bobertron was now 
called spender. They stood tall. They flew off in search of Ultra Magnus 
knowing that he must be warned of magmatrons return.
